elem_dict.text: From the heart of downtown to fashionable Back Bay, our Boston clubs are designed to inspire. Each location delivers the essential elements of well-being, including innovative classes, exceptional trainers, and now the Precision Running Lab, our breakthrough standalone running studio, only at Equinox Chestnut Hill.
